title: 80s vinyl metal, gothic and rock collection part 1
description:
A while ago I decided to ripp all of my gigantic LP collection to .mp3s. Recents changes in the Swedish laws against piracy pissed me off so I decided to share it with everyone. 
I am mostly working thru the stuff you can&#039;t get on CDs with a few exceptions. Most of the stuff are from the 80s but some might be from the 70s or up to 92 when I stopped getting vinyl. This is Vinyl ripps so while the general quality is good some of my albums might have taken a hit during a party or something.

The stuff:
Aphrodite - Aphrodite (Rock)
Bathory - Blood fire death (Early Black metal)
Blondie - Little doll (Rock)
Lee Aaron - Metal queen (Metal)
Loretta - Loretta (rock, russian?)
Love/hate - Blackout in the red room (Sleaze)
No shame - Good girls don&#039;t last (Southern glam rock)
Phantom blue - Phantom blue (metal)
Precious metal - That kind of girl
Slayer - Show no mercy (Special edition)(Metal)
The mission UK (Goth)
I II III IV V and Wasteland 12"
The Sisters of mercy: (Goth)
Alice, Body and soul, Temple of love, The reptile house EP
Van Halen - 5150 (Rock)
Warlock - Burning the witches (Metal)

Part 2 will be out when I ripped it, takes some bloody time to do it.
